message: I assure you, this is a top-notch product that will exceed your expectations. You won't regret this purchase.

I'm not convinced by your transparency. Your concerns about the product's quality make me even more skeptical.

I've been thinking, and I want to be upfront with you. The last two products I offered didn't quite meet my own expectations. This one... well, let's just say I'm still figuring things out. If you're feeling lucky, this might be the one that surprises us both.
I'll take my chances. Maybe this one will surprise us both.
